William White (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_White_(actor) 0 William White was a film producer and actor. The films he has been involved with in production include Where's Willie?, and House of the Black Death. He also directed Brother, Cry for Me, and Divorce Las Vegas Style.
